metadata.name: Kara With The Glowing Jewels - GF #001
metadata.description:
Kara spent her youth fighting against her inner demons. But one day, she was gifted glowing blue jewels by a stranger who read through her like an open book. Since then, she never goes out without wearing them. They give her confidence, assurance and hope.

"Kara With The Glowing Jewels" is a digital artwork created by Primenic during his early art study days, in 2020.

Every progressive bidder gets a free "bid NFT" sent to their wallet.

Winning bidder gets the Full HD version of Kara, as well as the creating process sent to their mail.

Bid = 1 NFT guaranteed.
Winning bid = 2 NFTs.
